```dockerfile
# Stage 1: Build frontend
FROM node:20-alpine AS frontend-builder

WORKDIR /app/frontend

COPY frontend/package*.json ./
RUN npm ci

COPY frontend/ .
RUN npm run build

# Stage 2: Build Python dependencies
FROM python:3.12-slim AS python-builder

WORKDIR /app

# Install system dependencies for building
RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
    libpq-dev \
    unixodbc-dev \
    && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

# Install Poetry
RUN pip install --no-cache-dir poetry

# Copy Poetry files
COPY pyproject.toml poetry.lock ./

# Install Python dependencies into a virtualenv
RUN poetry config virtualenvs.in-project true && \
    poetry install --no-dev --no-interaction --no-ansi

# Stage 3: Runtime image
FROM python:3.12-slim

LABEL maintainer="Analytics Platform Team" \
      description="Production-grade analytics platform with React frontend and Python backend"

# Install runtime system dependencies
RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
    libpq5 \
    unixodbc \
    curl \
    && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

# Create non-root user
RUN groupadd -g 1000 superset && \
    useradd -r -u 1000 -g superset superset

WORKDIR /app

# Copy frontend static assets from builder
COPY --from=frontend-builder /app/frontend/dist ./frontend/dist

# Copy Python dependencies from builder
COPY --from=python-builder /app/.venv ./.venv

# Copy application code
COPY . .

# Set ownership to non-root user
RUN chown -R superset:superset /app

# Switch to non-root user
USER superset

# Expose port
EXPOSE 8088

# Healthcheck
HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=10s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:8088/health || exit 1

# Set PATH to include virtualenv
ENV PATH="/app/.venv/bin:$PATH"

# Run application
CMD ["gunicorn", "-w", "4", "-b", "0.0.0.0:8088", "app:create_app()"]
